{"tid":163252,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[解夢]岩岩放紫晶上眉心冥想 之後發左幾秒夢","createTime":"2017-03-19T20:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T22:49:16.000Z","uid":84373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5ac8b753286564223499b11e4c8db78f9f894f","tid":163252,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T20:36:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n咁我半夜兩點幾冇野做 就返上床冥想<br />\n坐坐下就想訓低<br />\n之後就訓低 再放條紫水晶上眉心繼續冥想<br />\n之後有幾秒我就訓著左 就發左個夢<br />\n個夢好簡單<br />\n<br />\n有個紫色皮膚紅色頭髮好似LEGO咁嘅野露牙笑笑口打側身望住我 之後佢沉左洛地走左<br />\n個場景都係深暗紅<br />\n大約係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnw9a52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmnw9a52.png&h=798f366b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9C4MTsk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9C4MTsk.jpg&h=aedace15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沈左洛去之後我就醒左 <br />\n依家乜事都冇 <br />\n岩岩肚痛柯緊屎<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a410ce4fb8c9000b6c16aad694fcd793bfff9c8","tid":163252,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T20:44:08.000Z","msg":"辦定身後事"},{"pid":"b5d2227c28eab6072af0fb500d608ede4b105cf5","tid":163252,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T20:44:36.000Z","msg":"同埋下世唔好咁做啦"},{"pid":"2a7ab14d9f274de50fb19453ccd7d4211cbc35d3","tid":163252,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T20:54:32.000Z","msg":"好快你會搵到答案"},{"pid":"873016e5b06db6ac70d3896198eaac8cb7db3412","tid":163252,"uid":75242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T21:33:26.000Z","msg":"獲得入住和合石既資格"},{"pid":"e44a68a372dd0dcaa834a3093b491d96bac580bb","tid":163252,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T21:58:37.000Z","msg":"安已不<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111b2da173d4c1a5d84ca8ef6a698